deepl:Htpdate doesn't run as a daemon, i.original: Htpdate doesn't run as a daemon, it updates the time after an IP change, during system startup and the given intervals automatically.
deepl:Htpdate doesn't run as a daemon, i.translation: Htpdate non viene eseguito come demone, ma aggiorna automaticamente l'ora dopo un cambio di IP, all'avvio del sistema e a intervalli prestabiliti.
